highlights.text: “The Happy Song” by Imogen Heap is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Singapore, up 26 spots at #68.
“有一种遗憾叫我们” by 田园 has been on Viral Songs Singapore the longest, at 98 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Singapore. “Golden” is the highest at #1.
“1+1” by Naïka is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Singapore at #80.
